556
00:32:12.300 --> 00:32:14.930
Would you imagine oralmost believe,

557
00:32:14.930 --> 00:32:16.770
were't not that by greatpreservation

558
00:32:16.770 --> 00:32:17.800
we live to tell it,

559
00:32:17.800 --> 00:32:19.000
that the subtle traitorthis day

560
00:32:19.000 --> 00:32:20.400
