00:35:12.670 --> 00:35:14.530
And so, my lord, adieu.

619
00:35:14.530 --> 00:35:17.170
If you thrive well, bringthem to Baynard's Castle,

620
00:35:17.170 --> 00:35:18.530
where you will find mewell accompanied

621
00:35:18.530 --> 00:35:20.530
