00:36:30.000 --> 00:36:34.870
And mark how well thesequel hangs together.

636
00:36:36.500 --> 00:36:41.230
Eleven hours I have spentto write it over,

637
00:36:41.230 --> 00:36:44.430
for yesternight by Catesbywas it sent me.

638
00:36:45.670 --> 00:36:48.100
The precedent was full aslong a-doing.

639
00:36:50.030 --> 00:36:55.830
