00:37:10.770 --> 00:37:15.770
Yet who is so bold butsays he sees it not?

644
00:37:18.530 --> 00:37:23.570
Bad is the world, and allwill come to naught

645
00:37:23.570 --> 00:37:27.430
when such ill dealing mustbe seen in thought.

646
00:37:31.970 --> 00:37:34.200
How now? How now? What saythe citizens?

647
00:37:34.200 --> 00:37:36.000
Now, by the holy mother ofour Lord,

648
00:37:36.000 --> 00:37:38.300
the citizens are mum, saynot a word.

649
00:37:39.500 --> 00:37:41.670
Touched you the bastardyof Edward's children?

650
00:37:41.670 --> 00:37:42.730
I did.

651
00:37:42.730 --> 00:37:44.100
With his contract withLady Lucy

652
00:37:44.100 --> 00:37:46.070
and his contract by deputyin France,

653
00:37:46.070 --> 00:37:48.370
the insatiate greedinessof his desire

654
00:37:48.370 --> 00:37:50.370
and his enforcement of thecity wives,

655
00:37:50.370 --> 00:37:52.000
his tyranny for trifle,

656
00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:54.530
his own bastardy, as being got,your father then in France,

657
00:37:54.530 --> 00:37:57.430
and his resemblance beingnot like the duke.

658
00:37:57.430 --> 00:38:01.630
Withal, I did infer yourlineaments

659
00:38:01.630 --> 00:38:03.770
being the right idea ofyour father

660
00:38:03.770 --> 00:38:07.830
both in your form andnobleness of mind.

661
00:38:07.830 --> 00:38:09.900
Laid open all yourvictories in Scotland,

662
00:38:09.900 --> 00:38:12.070
your discipline in war,your wisdom in peace,

663
00:38:12.070 --> 00:38:15.230
your bounty, virtue, fairhumility.

664
00:38:15.230 --> 00:38:18.000
Indeed, left nothing fittingfor your purpose untouched

665
00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:19.600
or slightly handled indiscourse.

666
00:38:19.600 --> 00:38:21.270
And when mine oratory drewto an end,

667
00:38:21.270 --> 00:38:23.070
I bid them that did lovetheir country's good

668
00:38:23.070 --> 00:38:25.430
cry "God save Richard,England's royal king."

669
00:38:25.430 --> 00:38:26.670
And did they so?

670
00:38:26.670 --> 00:38:27.770
No.

671
00:38:27.770 --> 00:38:30.570
God help me, they spakenot a word

672
00:38:30.570 --> 00:38:32.630
but like dumb statues orbreathing stones,

673
00:38:32.630 --> 00:38:34.300
stared each on other andlooked deadly pale,

674
00:38:34.300 --> 00:38:35.770
which, when I saw, Ireprehended them

675
00:38:35.770 --> 00:38:38.170
and asked the mayor whatmeant this willful silence.

676
00:38:38.170 --> 00:38:39.470
His answer was,

677
00:38:39.470 --> 00:38:41.430
