717
00:40:21.870 --> 00:40:23.500
divinely bent tomeditation,

718
00:40:23.500 --> 00:40:26.300
and in no worldly suitswould he be moved

719
00:40:26.300 --> 00:40:28.800
to draw him from his holyexercise.

720
00:40:28.800 --> 00:40:31.930
Return, good Catesby, tothe gracious duke.

721
00:40:31.930 --> 00:40:35.470
Tell him myself, themayor, and aldermen

722
00:40:35.470 --> 00:40:37.670
in deep designs and matterof great moment,

723
00:40:37.670 --> 00:40:40.330
no less importing than ourgeneral good,

724
00:40:40.330 --> 00:40:44.830
