727
00:40:54.530 --> 00:40:57.530
He is not lolling on alewd love bed

728
00:40:57.530 --> 00:41:00.730
but on his knees atmeditation,

729
00:41:00.730 --> 00:41:04.370
not dallying with a braceof courtesans

730
00:41:04.370 --> 00:41:07.230
but meditating with twodeep divines,

731
00:41:07.230 --> 00:41:11.930
not sleeping to engrosshis idle body,

732
00:41:11.930 --> 00:41:16.200
but praying to enrich hiswatchful soul.

733
00:41:17.470 --> 00:41:21.170
Happy were England wouldthis virtuous prince

734
00:41:21.170 --> 00:41:24.200
take on his grace thesovereignty thereof.

735
00:41:24.200 --> 00:41:27.730
