768
00:43:29.900 --> 00:43:32.100
I do suspect I have donesome offense

769
00:43:32.100 --> 00:43:34.330
that seems disgracious inthe city's eye

770
00:43:34.330 --> 00:43:36.500
and that you come toreprehend my ignorance.

771
00:43:36.500 --> 00:43:39.730
You have, my lord!

772
00:43:39.730 --> 00:43:41.070
