775
00:43:45.830 --> 00:43:50.730
Know then it is your faultthat you resign thesupreme seat,

776
00:43:50.730 --> 00:43:52.470
the throne majestical,

777
00:43:52.470 --> 00:43:54.830
the sceptered office ofyour ancestors

778
00:43:54.830 --> 00:43:57.970
to the corruption of ablemished stock.

779
00:43:57.970 --> 00:44:00.530
Whilst in the mildness ofyour sleepy thoughts,

780
00:44:00.530 --> 00:44:03.130
